## StudyBuddyAI – Architecture & Pseudocode

This document describes the high-level flow and pseudocode for the `StudyBuddyAI-Frontend` and `StudyBuddyAI-Backend` projects.

---

## Frontend (StudyBuddyAI-Frontend)

### App Bootstrap

```text
